Windows building:

1. Download and install MinGW from here: http://www.mingw.org/

2. Download and install the nopoll library from here: http://www.aspl.es/nopoll/downloads/

3. Go into the project directory and run "make.bat".

 make


Running:

1. Make sure SPJS is already running and ChiliPeppr has already opened a connection to your machine.

2. Start the program
